{"id": 57911, "date": "2025-08-06T04:00:02", "date_gmt": "2025-08-06T11:00:02", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57911"}, "modified": "2026-05-12T13:48:02", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-12T20:48:02", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-6-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/06/kingdom-of-days-august-6-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 6"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1966: </strong>The Castiles play a teen dance at the Harris Gardens Firehouse in Union Beach, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3516\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1966-0806/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?fit=777%2C800&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"777,800\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1966-0806\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?fit=758%2C780&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3516 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?resize=758%2C780&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"780\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?w=777&amp;ssl=1 777w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?resize=291%2C300&amp;ssl=1 291w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?resize=768%2C791&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1966-0806.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20177\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1966-08-06/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?fit=1040%2C697&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1040,697\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1966-08-06\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?fit=758%2C508&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20177 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?resize=758%2C508&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?w=1040&amp;ssl=1 1040w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?resize=300%2C201&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?resize=1024%2C686&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-08-06.png?resize=768%2C515&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records the final take of his signature song, &#8220;Born to Run.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Wu4_zVxmufY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their fifth of a six-night stand at the Monmouth Arts Center in Red Bank.</p>\n<div id=\"v-bk2bc9sJ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/bk2bc9sJ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>On their day off during their three-night stand in Washington, DC, Bruce, Garry, and Clarence join former Steel Mill bandmate Robbin Thompson&#8217;s band on stage at the Bayou Club, where they play &#8220;Carol.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-FLDOBpP5-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/FLDOBpP5?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Beaver Brown on stage at Big Man&#8217;s West in Red Bank for four songs, including &#8220;Jersey Girl.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-xSF5lJF0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/xSF5lJF0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20178\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1982-08-06a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?fit=1256%2C1404&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1256,1404\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1982-08-06a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?fit=758%2C847&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20178 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?resize=758%2C847&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"847\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?w=1256&amp;ssl=1 1256w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?resize=268%2C300&amp;ssl=1 268w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?resize=916%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 916w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06a.png?resize=768%2C858&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20179\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1982-08-06b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06b.png?fit=536%2C1746&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"536,1746\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1982-08-06b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06b.png?fit=314%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20179 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06b.png?resize=536%2C1746&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"536\" height=\"1746\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06b.png?w=536&amp;ssl=1 536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06b.png?resize=92%2C300&amp;ssl=1 92w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1982-08-06b.png?resize=314%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 314w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 536px) 100vw, 536px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two of ten at the Brendan Byrne Arena in East Rutherford on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, &#8220;Spirit in the Night&#8221; makes its tour debut, and &#8220;No Surrender&#8221; is played in its third arrangement of the tour. This one will stick, and this specific performance (along with &#8220;Nebraska&#8221; from this show) will appear on the\u00a0<em>Live 1975-85\u00a0</em>box set. Additionally Bruce&#8217;s performance of &#8220;Trapped&#8221; from this show will be released the following year on the\u00a0<em>We Are the World</em> album, as well as on\u00a0<em>The Essential Bruce Springsteen\u00a0</em>in 2003. The entire show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QB3KnqP7ee4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Bq2-frOfTnk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Pu1t_CdBpw4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hPQ_LwBDs_U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-IjAQtMZl8M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rZU8BySmjRw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDrZU8BySmjRw\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dtp_kCpA8kY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDDtp_kCpA8kY\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fz3aDOBCpLc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>It&#8217;s Night Nine of eleven at the Brendan Byrne Arena in East Rutherford on World Tour 1992. Bruce dedicates &#8220;Human Touch&#8221; to Jeff Porcaro of Toto, who played drums on most of the\u00a0<em>Human Touch\u00a0</em>album and who passed away the previous day. The official video for &#8220;Leap of Faith&#8221; is filmed at this show, and the audio is released on the CD single.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ouWEZPkbznQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/coxsX4WjiNc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Also on this day, Entertainment Tonight airs a segment on Bruce&#8217;s new <em>Rolling Stone</em> cover story, on sale today. (If you have the Album Collection Volume 2, you have that cover story in your bonus book.)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z_Yn_n6QRWI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20181\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/rs636/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/RS636.jpg?fit=474%2C590&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"474,590\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RS636\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/RS636.jpg?fit=474%2C590&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20181 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/RS636.jpg?resize=474%2C590&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"474\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/RS636.jpg?w=474&amp;ssl=1 474w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/RS636.jpg?resize=241%2C300&amp;ssl=1 241w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1995:\u00a0</strong>Bruce guest stars with Bobby Bandiera at Cheers in Long Branch, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce opens Night Eleven of the fifteen-night opening stand of the U.S. Reunion Tour in East Rutherford with the first full-band &#8220;Adam Raised a Cain&#8221; in eleven years. Bruce also tour premieres &#8220;Be True&#8221; and ends the show with &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; &#8212; the first time Bruce has played an additional song after &#8220;Land of Hope and Dreams&#8221; on this tour.</p>\n<div id=\"v-iaNIgJvr-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/iaNIgJvr?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>The Rising Stadium Tour heads to Pennsylvania for four shows, starting with a single night at PNC Park in Pittsburgh, where Joe and Johnny Grushecky make their (by now) customary appearance.</p>\n<div id=\"v-kHydzsi1-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/kHydzsi1?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20183\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-08-06/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2003-08-06.png?fit=2599%2C1392&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2599,1392\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-08-06\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2003-08-06.png?fit=758%2C406&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20183 size-full\" src=\"https:/